44. Rudebeck PH, Buckley MJ, Walton ME, Rushworth MF: A role for the macaque anterior cingulate gyrus in social valuation. Science 2006, 313:1310-1312.
45. Mitchell JP, Macrae CN, Banaji MR: Dissociable medial  prefrontal contributions to judgments of similar and dissimilar
